node.title: 4 people survive medical helicopter crash in Pennsylvania
node.description: One of them was an infant, CBS Philly reports.
node.content: ["Four people have survived a medical helicopter crash in Delaware County, Pennsylvania, according to authorities. One of them was an infant, CBS Philadelphia reports.", "The medical chopper was heading to Children's Hospital of Philadelphia from Maryland when it crashed near the Drexel Hill United Methodist Church in Drexel Hill just before 1 p.m. Tuesday, CBS Philadelphia said.", "This story is developing and will be updated."]
